For over fifty years, Curley & Curley, P.C. has provided clients with quality, cost-effective litigation defense marked by a personal, hands-on approach to each case.




 



 



Civil Litigation Defense Law Firm
Curley & Curley P.C. is a civil litigation defense law firm with offices at 35 Braintree Hill Office Park, Braintree, MA. Our firm has extensive experience representing and counseling insurance companies, corporations and government agencies.
Our attorneys represent clients in all trial and appellate courts of the Commonwealth of Massachusetts, the United States District Court for the District of Massachusetts, the U.S. Appeals Court for the First Circuit, the U.S. Supreme Court, as well as the Massachusetts Commission Against Discrimination and many other state and federal administrative agencies. From time to time, our attorneys also appear in the state and federal courts of New Hampshire.
Our firm is AV®-Rated by Martindale-Hubbell® Peer-Review Ratings. We are listed in Martindale-Hubbell, Inc.'s Bar Register of Preeminent Lawyers.
Our areas of practice
Curley & Curley represents clients in the following areas:

Products Liability
Insurance Coverage
Premises Liability
Toxic Torts
Defense of Government Agencies
Employment Law, Discrimination, Sexual Harassment
General Civil Litigation
Automobile Torts
Construction Law
Business Disputes
Professional Liability
Appellate Advocacy

We are proud of our legacy and the service that we have consistently provided to our clients and to the community. If you need defense against a liability claim, contact Curley & Curley P.C. for a consultation. Our attorneys and staff look forward to speaking with you about your legal issue.
Call 617-523-2990 for a civil litigation defense law firm in Boston.




