CIVIL AND COMMERCIAL LITIGATION 





















 Our legal practice focuses on civil and commercial litigation.  Clients include large national corporations,
                                                         mid-sized regional companies, small businesses and individuals.    Formerly
                                                         associated with Cummings & Lockwood and Pillsbury Winthrop LLP, Stephen J. Curley has over twenty-two years of complex
                                                         civil and commercial litigation experience in Connecticut state and federal courts.  Our clients enjoy both large firm experience
                                                         and small firm attention.  Our fees have been discounted to permit even the smallest of businesses access to quality legal
                                                         counsel.    Contact Steve personally to discuss your legal needs.  Initial
                                                         consultations are free of charge and obligation.  
















